{"tid":1849981,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"視網膜脫落手術後可唔可以揸番車???","createTime":"2020-01-29T10:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T13:54:13.000Z","uid":336339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"16a80de9e7654b1ec67f42ad4cdd516f91cfc23b","tid":1849981,"uid":336339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"本身有揸開車番工,出左事之後就俾左屋企人做假日車咁揸,宜家肺炎咁勁,番放工都唔想同人迫巴士黨鐵,想揸番車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講番我既情況,做完手術成3個幾月了,眼鏡都配左副新既,睇野有少少變形,太遲睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覆診又唔記得問醫生可唔可以揸番車,又要等到下一次覆診先問到,我公立醫院做,一次覆診都成幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲出左事之後有揸番車呢?"},{"pid":"e9fe3909b7051aa86a5374cb5bad10b74ce313cf","tid":1849981,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"你揸番車應該覺得周圍環境慢左，小心駕駛就得。"},{"pid":"db7537e6c6e364b9191abd926d3e0f1c9462d902","tid":1849981,"uid":152557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fe3909b7051aa86a5374cb5bad10b74ce313cf","tid":1849981,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"你揸番車應該覺得周圍環境慢左，小心駕駛就得。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"頭文字D"},{"pid":"fabc168e210dfc9ac5c7317e5d2ddb6db7c77a97","tid":1849981,"uid":336339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9fe3909b7051aa86a5374cb5bad10b74ce313cf","tid":1849981,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"你揸番車應該覺得周圍環境慢左，小心駕駛就得。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"因為睇野愈來愈慢,老豆就捉左我去驗眼先發現出左事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8118bb5ca6f48241453000ded14f5c1286cd71","tid":1849981,"uid":336339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲答到凡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class